{"tid":1324970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好中計，去打元朗就群眾鬥群眾","createTime":"2019-07-16T17:15:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T23:19:51.000Z","uid":54303,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"69831247f588dcb6510c6d38303a92ce36555ac0","tid":1324970,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:15:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">我地主要敵人係港共殖民政權，再加中聯辦</span><br />\n次要敵人係無腦黑警<br />\n<br />\n藍絲、黑社會甚至熱普城都唔洗突登去理<br />\n郁佢地出師無名又無乜著數<br />\n唔好比機會政府同警犬休息<br />\n一定要針對性、持續性去施壓<br />\n<br />\n元朗等地我認為做下低成本既野就得<br />\n各位手足有危險要即走甚至扮藍絲<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n號外！<br />\n8chan又有過千隻汪汪既資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇下呀sir你地可以點捉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n壇主唔撚會理你<br />\n你亦唔知係邊位手足放上去<br />\n更加唔洗諗刪左條link啦 冇可能架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：支持警方執法，如果你地做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f218d39a32f327c7a7d17f15b932ef122c274754","tid":1324970,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:16:50.000Z","msg":"好佩服果位爆料既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e2ba82e0df9519748e684794aa62e8b2d641ca","tid":1324970,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:20:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d832812342eb9d7a2db2635b2b371304d24e6ec0","tid":1324970,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:32:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f27316c1005459b19732993668a45779d00e4ce","